    %% External to Control Plane
    User -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token"| K8sAPI

    %% Control Plane to Operator
    K8sAPI -->|"Watch events<br/>controller-runtime<br/>SA Token"| Operator

    %% Operator to Control Plane
    Operator -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA Token<br/>CRD CRUD"| K8sAPI

    %% Operator to Ray Head
    Operator -->|"HTTP/8265<br/>plaintext<br/>No Auth<br/>Job submit / Serve config"| HeadPod

